General Information

This Oil Enhances Creativity And Focus.

Also Useful For: Headaches, Arthritis, Rheumatic Pain And Muscular Aches And Pains.

A strong penetrating fresh minty herbal aroma with a camphoraceous undertone

Warnings

STORE BELOW 30C. NOT TO BE TAKEN ORALLY. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN.

Ingredients

Rosmarinus officinalis herb 1mL/mL

Directions

Adult: For the temporary relief of HEADACHES, ARTHRITIS, RHEUMATIC PAIN and MUSCULAR ACHES and PAINS: add 5 drops to 10mL base oil and massage onto affected area or add to bath. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner.
